  "label": "Imperium Nihilus",
  "description": "A vast region of the galaxy severed from Imperial light by the Cicatrix Maledictum, where astropathic communion and reliable warp routes collapse into fragmentary, perilous threads. Its star systems persist under intermittent void-traffic, predation, and isolation, with many worlds reduced to fortress enclaves or ungoverned dead zones between feuding powers. The heavens are dominated by storm-wracked empyrean phenomena, tainted nebulae, and long stretches of null-lit interstellar night where navigation depends on rare, contested beacons.",
